https://www.houstoniamag.com/health-and-wellness/best-massage-facial-day-spas-houston"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.tripadvisor.com/Attractions-g56062-Activities-c40-Katy_Texas.html"},{"type":"url","url":"https://medspaatvillagio.com/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.papercitymag.com/fashion/houston-best-spas-post-oak-hotel-trellis-four-seasons/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.besanctuary.com/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.houstonian.com/the-spa"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.thepostoakhotel.com/wellness/spa/"}]}},{"id":"ws_53f282cb-901b-9e31-9d66-dffc5dc1901b_call-a7fb428b-fc14-4465-a197-1066dea15196-4","type":"web_search_call","status":"completed","action":{"type":"search","query":"spas near River Oaks Houston alternatives","sources":[{"type":"url","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?cflt=spas&find_loc=River+Oaks%2C+Houston%2C+TX"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.besanctuary.com/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.tripadvisor.com/Attractions-g56003-Activities-c40-Houston_Texas.html"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.houstonian.com/press/seven-Houston-Spa-Centers-to-Help-You-Unwind"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.houstoniamag.com/health-and-wellness/best-massage-facial-day-spas-houston"}]}},{"id":"tco_53f282cb-901b-9e31-9d66-dffc5dc1901b_call-a7fb428b-fc14-4465-a197-1066dea15196-4","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"id":"tco_53f282cb-901b-9e31-9d66-dffc5dc1901b_call-a7fb428b-fc14-4465-a197-1066dea15196-3","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"content":[{"type":"output_text","text":"**Milk + Honey (also styled milk + honey) is a luxury day spa + medspa + salon at 2800 Kirby Drive, Suite A134, in Houston’s River Oaks area (west-central Houston).** It offers massages, facials, body treatments, HydraFacials, waxing, peels, medspa services (like Botox/fillers/lasers), nails, and salon services in an upscale setting.[[1]](https://milkandhoneyspa.com/locations/houston-location-hours/)[[1]](https://milkandhoneyspa.com/locations/houston-location-hours/)\n\nHere are strong alternatives in or near west Houston (focusing on River Oaks, Memorial, Uptown/Galleria-adjacent, and further west like Katy), emphasizing similar luxury day-spa experiences with massages, facials, and related services:\n\n- **Sanctuary Spa** (1701 S. Shepherd, Suite C, Houston, TX 77019) — Houston’s original day spa (since 1984), known for luxurious facials, therapeutic massages, hydrotherapy, and skin care in a convenient spot between River Oaks and Montrose. Highly rated for pampering.[[2]](https://www.besanctuary.com/)\n\n- **Trellis Spa at the Houstonian** (111 N. Post Oak Lane, Houston, TX 77024) — A large, Forbes-recognized luxury resort-style spa in the Memorial area (solid west Houston location) offering massages, facials, body treatments, waxing, hair services, and more in a European-villa setting with gardens.[[3]](https://www.trellisspa.com/)\n\n- **The Spa at the Post Oak Hotel** (1600 West Loop South, Houston, TX 77027) — Upscale hotel spa (Uptown/Galleria vicinity) with high-end treatments, including result-oriented medi-spa options, in a Forbes Five-Star setting.[[4]](https://www.thepostoakhotel.com/wellness/spa/)\n\n- **Hiatus Spa + Retreat** (San Felipe area) — Frequently listed among Houston’s top wellness spots for facials, massages, and skin treatments in a modern retreat atmosphere.[[5]](https://www.houstoniamag.com/health-and-wellness/best-massage-facial-day-spas-houston)\n\n**Further west options (Katy/Energy Corridor area):**\n- Spavia Cinco Ranch (Katy) — Luxury day spa with resort-like amenities, massages, and facials.[[6]](https://cincoranchtx.spaviadayspa.com/)\n- MedSpa at Villagio (Katy) — Combines medical spa treatments, salon services, and day spa experiences.[[7]](https://medspaatvillagio.com/)\n- Spa World Houston (Katy) — Popular Korean-style spa with baths, saunas, and relaxation areas (different vibe but great for extended wellness).[[5]](https://www.houstoniamag.com/health-and-wellness/best-massage-facial-day-spas-houston)\n\nOther nearby mentions from local “best of” lists include Mokara Spa at the Omni Houston (west side) and various hotel spas. Check recent reviews on Yelp or similar sites, as offerings and availability can change. Many allow online booking—compare menus for specific treatments like facials or medspa services that match what you like at Milk + Honey.[[8]](https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Luxury+Spa&find_loc=Houston%2C+TX)\n\nIf you have preferences (e.g., specific services, budget, or exact neighborhood), I can refine these suggestions!","logprobs":[],"annotations":[{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://milkandhoneyspa.com/locations/houston-location-hours/","start_index":335,"end_index":403,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://milkandhoneyspa.com/locations/houston-location-hours/","start_index":403,"end_index":471,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.besanctuary.com/","start_index":980,"end_index":1015,"title":"2"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.trellisspa.com/","start_index":1317,"end_index":1351,"title":"3"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.thepostoakhotel.com/wellness/spa/","start_index":1578,"end_index":1630,"title":"4"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.houstoniamag.com/health-and-wellness/best-massage-facial-day-spas-houston","start_index":1806,"end_index":1898,"title":"5"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://cincoranchtx.spaviadayspa.com/","start_index":2049,"end_index":2094,"title":"6"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://medspaatvillagio.com/","start_index":2198,"end_index":2234,"title":"7"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.houstoniamag.com/health-and-wellness/best-massage-facial-day-spas-houston","start_index":2379,"end_index":2471,"title":"5"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Luxury+Spa&find_loc=Houston%2C+TX","start_index":2823,"end_index":2901,"title":"8"}]}],"id":"msg_53f282cb-901b-9e3